Ibyago byo kwandura coronavirus (COVID-19) mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu w'u Bwongereza, kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020
Ibyabaye byatewe n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) bigaragaza imiterere nk'iyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza, byerekana ko nubwo mu bihugu bitandukanye, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibihamya bitangwa n'u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kongera imyiteguro yabo ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bazagomba kwitabwaho mu buryo bwa muganga, cyane cyane ku barwayi bakomeye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, havuzwe ko hari icyorezo cy'ibicurane kitaramenyekana mu kimera cyacyo cyabaye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko hari umuntu utanga virusi nshya ya coronavirus yahindutse virusi ya mbere y'uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bwitwa SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-COV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yongeye kwanduza abagore indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibipimo bigaragaza ko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero, yaba ifitanye isano n'uburwayi bw'ibihaha cyangwa nta ho ihuriye na bwo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu barwayi 14%, COVID-19 iba icyorezo gikeneye gucumbikirwa mu bitaro mu gihe 6% y'abarwayi barwaye indwara zikeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro biturutse kuri COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, dusesengura impinduka mu mibare ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'u Burayi/Akarere k'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza) tukabigereranya n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'iy'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu bitandukanye kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu gikurikirana iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari yo yabaye iya mbere mu Burayi yemeje icyorezo cya COVID-19 hashingiwe ku bimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, Ubufaransa bwatangaje bwa mbere abantu batatu banduye coronavirus ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse baturutse i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyamaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 bigize EU/EEA na UK, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza uyu munsi, habonetse abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye 1,727 batangajwe, hamwe n'abanduye 17,750. n'abapfuye 1,441 mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona imibare y'ibanze n'ibyavuye mu bikorwa by'abanduye COVID-19
Mu Kigo cy'Uburayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), hatangajwe imibare ya COVID-19 mu gihugu cyose ku isi, ikururwa gusa n'ibikoresho byemewe n'amategeko nka minisiteri y'ubuzima y'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu na OMS na OMS, kandi ivugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kuyigereranya n'iy'u Butaliyani.
Nk'ikigereranyo cy'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, twabaririje iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, bityo dukurikije icyiciro cya COVID-19, muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, hagati ya 1 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twatangije kandi imibare y'ibarura ry'ubwandu buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'igitondo ugereranyije n'iy'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Ihinduka ry'iminsi 14 y'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza muri rusange rikurikirwa n'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 yatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho igenda yiyongera cyane ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibimenyetso by'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'imibare y'abatangajwe ko banduye muri Italiya, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye ko hari ukwiyongera kw'imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 (Ibikoresho by'ibanze).
Ishusho ya 2 igaragaza ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'ubwo mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ivuga ko guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'ibyo mu karere k'ubutaka bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byari bimaze gutanga raporo y'ubwandu bw'iki cyorezo ugereranyije n'ubwo mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abandura COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibyagarutsweho mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 byerekana ko iki cyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ibi kandi n'ubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, mu bisubizo by'ubuzima bw'abaturage, kandi bishobora kuba bifite ibibazo bitandukanye mu bihugu n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo barebe COVID-19, harimo no kubona ibizamini.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwuzuye.
Amakuru y'abarwayi bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 na/cyangwa mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe ubu araboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% na 1% gusa, bakurikije uko babyifuza (amakuru ntabwo agaragaza).
Ariko kandi, bigomba gutangwa mu buryo buhuje n'amakuru yo kugenzura arimo agaragaza umubare w'abandura n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu burwayi bwo mu mutwe n'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe mu Burayi, buva ku burwayi bwa 29.2 mu Budage bugera ku burwayi bwa 4.2 ku baturage 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo cyangwa ubutaka bwinshi kurusha u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda byita ku barwayi bakomeye ku baturage 100.000 mu 2010-11).
Imiterere y'ibaruramari ishingiye ku kwiyongera kw'ibigo nderabuzima, hamwe n'imibare y'igihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'ubwiganze bw'abari mu bitaro kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19 gihura na &gt; > 90% by'ibyago byo kurara mu buriri bw'ubuvuzi, byatanzwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu rya ECDC ry'ibyavuye mu isuzuma ry'ibyago bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko ubwandu bufite umwanya munini mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bya EU/EEA na UK, ndetse n'ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwimbitse bikunze gufasha abaturage bo mu karere kazwi, amakuru ajyanye n'ubwandu n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi byaba byiza aboneka ku rwego rw'ibanze rw'ibanze rw'ibanze rw'ibaruramari 2 (NUTS-2).
Inyigisho zo mu Butaliyani n'ibyagiye bibaho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kwitegura uburyo SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwira mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, ndetse n'ubundi buryo bwo kwita ku barwayi, nk'uko bigenda mu bice byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu bipimo biherutse gukorwa na ECDC, kwihuta, gukora neza no gushyiraho gahunda yuzuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, hamwe no guhindukira kuva ku kwiyongera kugera ku kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera byihuse kw'umubare w'abandura bidashobora guha abajyanama n'ibitaro umwanya uhagije wo gusobanukirwa, kwakira no guhuza uburyo bwo gukora mbere y'igihe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku byorezo kandi bwerekana ingamba zo kugabanya ingaruka z'ibyorezo.
Hariho umwanya muto mu gihe ibihugu bifite uburyo bwo kongera imbaraga mu mihati yo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ingaruka ku buzima.
Urebye ibi, birashoboka ko sisitemu y'ubuzima mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bya EU/EEA ishobora guhura n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 kandi cyandura abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, cyabaye icyago gikomeye ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi imwe, SARS-CoV, yatumye SARS yandura mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo ishobora kwandura mu nyamaswa kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Nyamara COVID-19 ifite uburwayi buciriritse kandi buhitana abantu benshi kurusha SARS ariko ni indwara yandura cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Bitewe n'umubare munini w'ibitabo bivuga ku cyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera, iyi ngingo igerageza gutanga ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku iterambere ry'ikibazo cyo gushakisha vuba.
Tuziga ibintu by'ibanze birebana n'indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, impamvu zitera, za virusi, ibijyanye n'ubushakashatsi, ubuvuzi, uko umuntu ashobora kuyirwara n'uko yayirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi nama izafasha mu gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo muri iyi minsi mikuru yose ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'icyorezo.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003; bityo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, naho indwara ihura na yo yitwa CoV-19 Disease (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyihuta cyane kigakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse kigakwira no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yateye abantu barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abarwayi barenga 40.000 barakize ndetse abarwayi barenga 3,000 barapfuye.
"WHO yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari ""umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage"" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye cyane kurusha iterabwoba".
Nk'uko tubikesha PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 200 kuri COVID-19 harimo virologie, épidémiologie, étiologie, diagnostic, na traitement kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yashyiraga ahagaragara urutonde rw'indwara yaciwe mu barwayi benshi.
Iyi ngingo igerageza gusobanura muri make ibyakozwe mu bushakashatsi ku ngingo nshya kandi zikura vuba.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS hamwe na CoV yindi iteza iyi ndwara, indwara yo mu muhogo yo mu karere k'Abarabu (MERS, mu 2012).
Nanone kandi, turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana n'uburyo bwo gukingira indwara n'uko twazivanaho, ndetse turebe n'ibindi bibazo bikiriho.
CoVs mu buryo busanzwe zifatwa nk'indwara zidakira abantu, ahanini zigira uruhare mu 15% by'indwara z'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'ibyorezo bibiri by'indwara z'ubwandu bw'umuntu, ari byo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, byateje icyorezo cya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, bikurikirana, kandi bihita byikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu bifite ubukana bukomeye n'urupfu.
Bityo rero, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka ya muntu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1,1, icyorezo cya mbere cy'ubwandu bw'ibicurane cyatangiye guturuka i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 mu Bushinjacyaha bw'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, icyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi cya CoV cyongeye gukorwa.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020 nibwo habonetse amakuru y'uko umuntu wa mbere yanduye indwara ya Wuhan.
Hagati aho, iyo ndwara yageze mu migi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, inzego z'ubuzima zatangaje ko abantu bashobora kwandura.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe, ndetse n'ingendo rusange zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwakozwe ku murwayi bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bari bafitanye isano ya hafi n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, ryibonekeza nk'aho ari ho hatangiriye kwandura indwara zaturutse ku nyamaswa.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko ku isi hose hari ikibazo cy'icyorezo.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyo ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi (Igice cya 2).
Uko ibintu bigenda byihuta, ni na ko bigenda birushaho kwiyongera.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo ku barwayi 8,866 barimo 4,021 bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19 byatangajwe ko amakuru mashya yerekeranye n'icyorezo ari uku gukurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Abantu b'imyaka yose bashobora kwandura SARS, ariko abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65 ni bo bayirwara cyane.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abandura bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 50, bake cyane bakaba bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa ni bo banduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane abagabo (0.31/100.000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100.000).
COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bice by'iburengerazuba no mu nkengero za Hubei.
COVID-19 imara iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva itangiye kugeza igihe igaragazwa.
Igihe cy'ubwandu ni iminsi 4,8 (3.0-7.2).
Igihe cyo kuvuka kugeza ku rupfu, ugereranyije ni iminsi 9,5 (4.8-13)
