Hari ibihe bitanu ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu atagerwaho n'indwara y'ubwonko: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (kugeza, kudakoresha isuku), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana (kuhindura isuku), mbere yo kumugaburira, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gukaraba ibiryo cyangwa gukorakora inyama mbi, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Indi mimerere igaragaza ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki neza kugira ngo yirinde gukwirakwiza indwara, ni mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gukaraba ikintu cyangwa gukomeretsa; nyuma yo gukora ku magufwa y'inyamaswa cyangwa ku magufwa y'inyamaswa; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu ntibakunda gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
