Kwirinda akaga ko mu kazi kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19
Gukurikirana ibyago byo mu kazi bituruka kuri COVID-19 birimo kwirinda mu kazi n'uburyo bwo kwirinda ibyago byo kwirinda abantu kwandura coronavirus COVID-19 mu 2019.
Kugenzura neza akaga ko ku kazi biterwa n'imiterere y'aho ukorera n'aho ukorera, hashingiwe ku kureba akaga kari mu karere ka virusi, ubukana bw'icyorezo mu baturage, n'akaga kari mu bakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi (OSHA), ibyago byo kwandura indwara ziterwa no guhura n'abantu benshi ndetse n'abandi bakozi, harimo kwirinda kwandura indwara, gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka, guhumeka buri munsi, gusukura no guhanagura indwara mu kazi.
Ibikorwa bishobora guteza ubwandu birimo abantu bagomba guhura cyangwa guhura n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cyangwa ingendo zo mu mahanga.
Muri ibyo hakubiyemo abakozi bakorana n'abantu benshi, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu higanje abantu benshi n'ahantu hakunze kugurishirizwa ibintu.
Kugenzura ibyago kuri aya matsinda, usibye kwirinda kwandura birimo, guhumeka ukoresheje imyanda ya filtre ya microbe, gupfuka no kugira ibikoresho byayo ku mubiri mu gihe umuntu yaba arwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ibona ko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakozi bo mu rugo bagaragaye ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bikongera ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyo abakozi bakurikije amabwiriza yo kumena aerosol, cyangwa gukusanya cyangwa gutunganya ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19.
Ibimenyetso by'akaga ku bakozi bihuza n'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi nk'icyumba cy'umuyaga, n'ibikoresho by'uburinzi ku bakozi bihuje n'akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora gutera ibibazo byinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kudakora bitewe n'uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi irashobora guhinduka, harimo no kumenya ubwoko bw'ibicuruzwa bikenewe, n'uburyo ibicuruzwa bizatangwa (Nk'ubucuruzi bwijoro cyangwa serivisi yo gutwara imodoka).
Amaherezo, ibikoresho byoherezwa ku migabane ifite ubwandu bukabije bwa COVID-19 bishobora guhagarara.
Guteganya neza bigabanya ibyago byo mu kazi, harimo aho umuntu yandurira, ibibazo by'ibyago bituruka mu rugo n'imimerere y'abaturage, n'ibibazo by'ibyago byo mu kazi nk'imyaka cyangwa indi ndwara ikomeye.
Zigaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura ibiza, n'uburyo bwo kwirinda imyifatire nk'iyo ishobora guterwa n'icyorezo.
Gahunda y'ubwandu bw'indwara zandura n'uburyo bwo kubwirana bishobora kuba ingingo z'inama z'igihugu cyangwa iz'igihugu.
Amategeko yo kumenya amakuru ku cyorezo arimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu bakozi, kurinda ubuzima bw'abantu bafatwa nk'abagomba gufatwa, kuvugurura gahunda y'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka ku bandi bantu.
Indwara y'ibicurane yagize ingaruka mu duce dukorerwamo imirimo y'ubucuruzi.
Gukurikirana impanuka ni uburyo bukoreshwa mu kugenzura niba akazi gafite umutekano n'ubuzima bwiza ku birebana n'impanuka z'ibyiciro by'ingenzi.
Aho COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kuyirinda ni ubwubatsi, gukurikiraho imikorere, hanyuma ibyangombwa by'ubwirinzi.
Imibare y'ubwubatsi ishingiye ku kwirengagiza abakozi mu byugarije akazi bidashingiye ku mico y'abakozi, kandi ni umuti uhenze ushyirwa mu bikorwa.
Inteko nyobozi yahindura imimerere y'akazi n'imikorere, ibyo bikaba byasabaga ko umukozi ashyiraho imihati.
Ibikoresho byo kwirinda (PPE) byitwa ko ari nk'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi budafite imbaraga ariko bishobora kugabanya ubwandu, ariko bishobora kugabanya ubwandu.
PPE yose igomba gutoranywa mbere y'uko umukozi agerwaho n'impanuka, gushyirwa mu mwanya wayo neza (Miss respirator), igihe n'uburyo, no kugenzurwa kenshi, guhindurwa iyo ifashe no kuvanaho, gukaraba, no gushyirwa mu mwanya mwiza kugirango umusatsi utinda guturika.
Dukurikije Itegeko ry'Amerika ryita ku buzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), ubukana bw'ibyago byo mu kazi ni uko umukozi atagirana imishyikirano n'abandi bakozi.
Gahunda z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zasabwe ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo harimo gukaraba intoki buri gihe, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukora imashini zo guhumeka zifite ibyuma bipfukaho umwotsi n'ubushyuhe, gutanga ibyangombwa n'ibisigazwa by'imyanda, gutegura aho bakorera mu rugo cyangwa guhindurira imyanda iyo bibaye ngombwa, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza isuku mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubwandu no kwangiza imiterere y'akazi.
Gushakisha byihuse no gushyira mu kato abanduye ni bwo buryo bwiza bwo kurinda ubuzima bw'abakozi, abakiriya n'abakozi bo mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyasabye abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara yo guhumeka kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bakira, niba ibimenyetso by'umuriro bikomeje amasaha 24 batarabona umuti cyangwa ibimenyetso by'indwara bitagakira kandi ikiruhuko cyo kurwara gihagaze neza, abakozi bagomba kuguma mu rugo bagakurikirana umurwayi kuko bazi gahunda.
Ku bw'ibya OSHA, abakora ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bafite ibyago byo kwandura birimo abakenera kwegera cyangwa guhura n'abantu bari hagati ya metero esheshatu (1.8 m) bataramenyekana cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe no gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu baturage mu bigo by'ubucuruzi, cyangwa bitewe n'umuntu wagiye mu kindi gihugu mu gace karimo ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
